    π⁴ terms           (= 1024 R₄² — geometric at higher order)
    π²ln(2) terms     (same class as A₂ geometric piece)
    Li₄(1/2) terms    (NEW: polylogarithm at x=1/2)
    ln⁴(2) terms      (NEW: fourth power of ln2)

  Every π² → 32R₄, every π⁴ → 1024R₄².
  The geometric content proliferates but remains separable.

  A₃ decomposition would require the full Laporta-Remiddi
  analytic result with all coefficients. This is known but
  lengthy. The A₂ decomposition demonstrates the method.

